title: Element Make It Count 2015 - Wildcard
description:
Win a trip to compete in the Element "Make it Count" Finals! 

Winners will be announced the first week of June.

1. Post a 15 sec. video of you at your local park on Instagram or Twitter
2. Hashtag #elementmakeitcount and #liveyours 
3. Include your city, state and country. 
Good Luck!!!
